<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Investona | FIRE Kalkulačka pro IT</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 font-sans antialiased">
    <div class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl w-full bg-gray-800 shadow-2xl rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex flex-col md:flex-row">
            
            <!-- Value Proposition (Levá strana) -->
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900 to-gray-900 flex flex-col justify-center">
                <div class="uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-400 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Dark Ops Lab: IT Segment</div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Optimalizujte cashflow. Akcelerujte nezávislost.</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Nechcete sedět u kódu do 65 let. Získejte náš framework pro ochranu B2B příjmů a výpočet FIRE (Financial Independence) metrik.</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm">
                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"></path></svg> Data-driven investiční přístup</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-blue-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"></path></svg> Ochrana před inflační degradací</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Lead Form (Pravá strana) -->
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 p-10 bg-white">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Získejte přístup</h2>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Zadejte kontakt, obratem posíláme přístup ke kalkulačce.</p>
                
                <!-- ZDE VLOŽTE URL MAKE.COM WEBHOOKU -->
                <form action="VASE_MAKE_COM_WEBHOOK_URL" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
                    <!-- Skrytý tag pro CRM -->
                    <input type="hidden" name="segment" value="IT_Freelancer">
                    
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Celé jméno</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name" required class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 text-gray-900">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Telefonní číslo</label>
                        <input type="tel" name="phone" required class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 text-gray-900">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">E-mail</label>
                        <input type="email" name="email" required class="mt-1 block w-full px-3 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 text-gray-900">
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="w-full flex justify-center py-3 px-4 border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">
                        Odeslat data
                    </button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
